            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Good condition. The omicron at the beginning of the text inscribing an abstract cross, is probably influenced by the decorative art of the manuscripts. The words οὐράνιον, ἄρτον are misspelled. Αccents and breathings with errors. The inscription is from the Prayer of the Prothesis. 
</p>
